attributes.name: OIC - Girls Development Clinic January 31 2026
attributes.description:
Girls Development Clinic

The Girls Development Clinic is designed to encourage girls of all skill levels to participate in an all-girls skills clinic each week.

This is not a skating class.

Participants must have completed Youth Hockey 123 or equivalent at minimum.

Full hockey gear is required.

Coaches: Tracey Roberts, various Bears coaching staff
